    c"No, I've got no idea who he is."
    a"Ok then, we'll have to pick up the pace and get to somewhere else."
    "After going further along it gets close to sun down but they are still following us so I lead Kunikada into the forest on the outskirts of the city."
    "I actually remember this place, Maeko and I used to play around here as kids."
    

  
